                <mxCell id="note-hybrid" value="&lt;b&gt;⚠ Azure Local Hybrid Note&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Session hosts are ON-PREMISES (Azure Local logical network).&lt;br&gt;Private endpoints are in an AZURE VNET (Azure region).&lt;br&gt;ExpressRoute or S2S VPN required for PE connectivity.&lt;br&gt;On-prem DNS must forward to Azure DNS Private Resolver.&lt;br&gt;Default: private_endpoints_enabled = false" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#FFECB3;strokeColor=#FF8F00;fontSize=9;align=left;spacingLeft=8;" parent="1" vertex="1">
